    <p align="center"><b><i>K&#257;p&#275;c daudzi kristiesi tom&#275;r nepaz<font face="Times New Roman">&#299;</font>st s&#257;du gar<font face="Times New Roman">&#299;</font>gi 
    bag&#257;tu dzivi?</i></b><br>
    </p>
    <div align="center"><center><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" background="images/spirback.gif" bgcolor="#BFBFFF"><b>
        <font size="5">2</font></b><font size="5">. </font><font size="4"><b>
        Mies&#299;gais kristietis nesp&#275;j dz&#299;vot s&#257;du pilnv&#275;rt&#299;gu kristiesa </b>
        </font><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font size="4"><b>dz&#299;vi.</b></font></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    </center></div><p align="left">T&#257;ds cilv&#275;ks ir p&#257;rliecin&#257;ts, ka var dz&#299;vot 
krist&#299;gu dzivi, vair&#257;k pa&#316;aujoties <br>
uz saviem sp&#275;kiem nek&#257; uz Dievu.</p>
    A. Vips ir aizmirsis vai ari nemaz nepaz&#299;st Dieva milestibu, piedosanu un 
sp&#275;ku <br>
<b><font color="#000080">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (Rom. 5, 8-10; Ebr. 10, 1-25; 
1. J&#257;&#326;a 1;2, 1-3; 2. P&#275;t. 1, 9; Ap. d. 1, 8).</font></b><br>
      <p>B. Vi&#326;a gar&#299;g&#257; dz&#299;ve ir 
      <font face="Times New Roman">&#316;</font>oti nestabila - pac&#275;lumi nep&#257;rtraukti mijas ar 
      kritieniem.<br>
      </p>
C. Mies&#299;gais cilv&#275;ks nesaprot pats sevi, grib r&#299;koties pareizi, bet to nesp&#275;j.<br>
      <p>D. S&#257;ds cilv&#275;ks neprot dz&#299;vot krist&#299;gu dz&#299;vi, 
      g&#363;stot jaunus sp&#275;kus 
      Sv&#275;taj&#257; <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Giar&#257; <b><font color="#000080">(1. Kor. 3, 1-3; Rom. 7, 
      15-24; 8, 7; Gal. 5, 16-18).</font></b></p>
    <p><br>
    <b>Mies&#299;gajam cilv&#275;kam</b> parasti liel&#257;k&#257; vai maz&#257;k&#257; m&#275;r&#257; piem&#299;t s&#257;das 
    iez&#299;mes:<br>
    </p>
<div align="center">
