</div>
    <p align="center"><b><i>Vien&#299;go atrisin&#257;jumu sniedz s&#299; paties&#299;ba...</i></b><br>
&nbsp;</p>
    <div align="center"><center><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" background="images/spirback.gif" bgcolor="#BFBFFF"><b>
        <font size="5">3. J</font><font size="4">&#275;zus ir apsolijis pilnv&#275;rt&#299;gu 
        un bag&#257;tu dz&#299;vi tiem, kas to </font></b><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b><font size="4">piln&#299;gi nodod Sv&#275;t&#257; Gara 
        vad&#299;bai.</font></b></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    </center></div><p>Sv&#275;t&#257; Gara vad&#299;tas dzives valdnieks ir J&#275;zus Kristus.<font color="#000000"><br>
    </font>
<p><font color="#000000"><b>A</b>. Par kristiesiem m&#275;s k<font face="Times New Roman">&#316;</font>&#363;stam 
Sv&#275;t&#257; Gara darbibas ietekm&#275;.
        </font><b><font color="#000080">(J&#257;&#326;a ev. 3, 1-8)</font></b><font color="#000000">. 
Vi&#326;s iem&#257;jo katr&#257; <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; tic&#299;gaj&#257; no t&#257; atpest&#299;sanas jeb otrreiz&#275;j&#257;s 
piedzimsanas br&#299;za
        </font><b><font color="#000080">(J&#257;&#326;a ev. 1, 12; Kol. 2, 9-10; J&#257;&#326;a ev.
<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 14, 16-17)</font></b><font color="#000000">. Bet tas nenoz&#299;m&#275;, ka visi kristiesi 
pak&#316;auj
savu dz&#299;vi Sv&#275;t&#257; Gara vad&#299;bai, Vi&#326;a sp&#275;kam.<br>
<br>
        <b>B</b>. Sv&#275;tais Gars ir neizsikstoss avots pilnv&#275;rtigai un brinis&#311;igai 
dzivei
        </font><b><font color="#000080">(J&#257;&#326;a ev. 7, 37-39)</font></b><font color="#000000"><br>
        <br>
        <b>C</b>. Sv&#275;tais Gars n&#257;ca, lai pagodin&#257;tu J&#275;zu Kristu
        </font><b><font color="#000080">(J&#257;&#326;a ev. 16, 1-15)</font></b><font color="#000000">. 
Tikai Sv&#275;t&#257; Gara vadits kristietis <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; var b&#363;t patiess Kristus m&#257;ceklis.<br>
        <br>
        D. Pirms savas uz&#326;emsanas debes&#299;s J&#275;zus sac&#299;ja, ka Sv&#275;tais Gays dos mums 
sp&#275;ku liecin&#257;t par Vi&#326;u
        </font><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font color="#000000">cilv&#275;kiem
        </font><b><font color="#000080">(Ap. d. 1, 1-9)</font></b><font color="#000000">.</font></p>
    <p align="center"><b><i>K&#257; m&#275;s varam uz&#326;emt Sv&#275;to Garu?</i></b></p>
    <div align="center"><center><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" background="images/spirback.gif" bgcolor="#BFBFFF"><b>
        <font size="5">4</font><font size="4">. Tikai tic&#299;b&#257; m&#275;s varam uz&#326;emt 
        Sv&#275;to Garu. Tikai tad <br>
        s&#257;kas t&#257; p&#257;rpiln&#257; dz&#299;ve, ko Kristus ir apsol&#299;jis katram <br>
        tic&#299;gajam.</font></b></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    </center></div><p><font color="#000000">]&#363;s varat pie&#326;emt Sv&#275;to Garu ticsi 
saj&#257; br&#299;di, ja vien:<br>
    <br>
<b>A</b>. Patiesi v&#275;laties nodot savu dz&#299;vi Sv&#275;t&#257; Gara vad&#299;bai un smelties 
jaunus sp&#275;kus Vi&#326;&#257; <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
    </font><b><font color="#000080">(Mateja ev. p, 6; ]&#257;&#326;a ev. 7, 37-39)</font></b><font color="#000000"><br>
        <br>
        <b>B</b>. Noz&#275;lojat savus gr&#275;kus. Pateicieties tic&#299;b&#257; Dievam, ka Vi&#326;s ir 
piedevis visus j&#363;su gr&#275;kus - bijusos, <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; esosos un n&#257;kosos - Kvistus n&#257;ves d&#275;&#316;
    </font><b><font color="#000080">(Kol. 2, 13-15; 1. J&#257;&#326;a 1;2, 1-3;
Ebr. 10,1-17).</font></b><font color="#000000"><br>
        <br>
        <b>C</b>. Nododiet piln&#299;gi visu savu dz&#299;vi Dieva zi&#326;zi
    </font><b><font color="#000080">(Rom. 12, 1-2).</font></b><font color="#000000"><br>
        <br>
    </font><b>D</b>. Tic&#299;b&#257; uz&#326;emiet Sv&#275;to Garu saska&#326;&#257; ar: <blockquote>
          <p>1. <b>Vi&#326;a pav&#275;li </b>- topiet Gara pilni. &quot;Un neapreibinieties ar 
          v&#299;nu, <br>
          no k&#257; ce<font face="Times New Roman">&#316;</font>as izlaid&#299;ga dz&#299;ve, bet 
          topiet Gara pilni.&quot; <b><font color="#000080">(Efez. 5, 18)</font></b></p>
          <p>2. <b>Vi&#326;a apsol&#299;jumu</b> - Vi&#326;s vienm<font face="Times New Roman">&#275;</font>r atbild&#275;s uz m&#363;su l&#363;gsanu, 
          ja <br>
          vien l&#363;cdzam p&#275;c Vi&#326;a pr&#257;ta. &quot;Un s&#299; pal&#257;viba mums ir uz Vi&#326;u, ka <br>
          Vi&#326;s klausa m&#363;s, ja ko l&#363;dzam p&#275;c Vfi&#326;a pr&#257;ta. Ja zin&#257;m, ka Vi&#326;s <br>
          m&#363;s klausa, ko vien l&#363;dzam, tad zin&#257;m, ka sa&#326;emam to, ko esam <br>
          no Vi&#326;a l&#363;gusi.&quot; <b><font color="#000080">(1. J&#257;&#326;a 5, 14-15)</font></b></p>
        </blockquote>
    <p><b><i>Tic&#299;ba acrod savu izpausmi l&#363;gsan&#257;...</i></b></p>
    <div align="center"><center><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><p align="center"><b><font size="4">
        K&#257; mums l&#363;gt, lai taptu Sv&#275;t&#257; Gara pilni?</font></b></p>
        <p>Tikai tic&#299;b&#257; m&#275;s varam uz&#326;emt Sv&#275;to Garu. V iena no tic&#299;bas izpausm&#275;m
        <br>
        ir l&#363;gsana. M&#363;su l&#363;gsana var&#275;tu b&#363;t, piem&#275;ram, s&#257;da:</p>
        <blockquote>
          <p><i>Debesu T&#275;vs! Es noz&#275;loju, ka esmu pats centies vad&#299;t savu dz&#299;vi, 
          t&#257;d&#275;j&#257;di gr&#275;kodams pret Tevi, p&#257;rk&#257;pdams Tavu gribu. Es pateicos Tev, 
          ka Tu esi piedevis rnanus gr&#275;kus, jo J&#275;zus mira pie krusta ari manu 
          gr&#275;ku d&#275;<font face="Times New Roman">&#316;</font>. Es l&#363;dzu Kristu, lai 
          Vi&#326;s ie&#326;em vietu manas dzives troni. Pildi mani ar Sv&#275;to Garu, k&#257; Tu 
          esi apsolijis katram, kas to I&#363;gs ticib&#257;. Es to l&#363;dzu J&#275;zus Kristtu 
          v&#257;rtl&#363;. Un, apliecinot savu tic&#299;bu, es tagad pateicos Tev, ka Tu vadi 
          manu dzivi un pildi mani ar Sv&#275;to Garu. <font face="Times New Roman">&#256;</font>men.</i><br>
          </p>
        </blockquote>
        <p>Vai sie v&#257;rdi izsaka j&#363;su person&#299;g&#257;s izj&#363;tas' Ja tas t&#257; ir, tad 
        pazemojieties <br>
        l&#363;gsan&#257;, un Dievs pild&#299;s j&#363;s ar Sv&#275;to Garu tiesi sobrid.</p>
        <hr>
        <p align="left"><b><font size="4">K&#257; m&#275;s varam b&#363;t p&#257;rliecin&#257;ti, ka 
        m&#363;su dzivi vada
        Sv&#275;tais Gars? </font></b></p>
        <p>Vai j&#363;s l&#363;dz&#257;t Dievu, lai Vi&#326;s pilda j&#363;s ar Sv&#275;to Garu? Vai esat 
        p&#257;rliecin&#257;ti, ka Vi&#326;s izpild&#299;ja j&#363;su l&#363;gumu? K&#257;d&#275;<font face="Times New Roman">&#316;</font> 
        j&#363;s esat p&#257;rliecin&#257;ti? T&#257;d&#275;<font face="Times New Roman">&#316;,</font> ka 
        Dievam un Vi&#326;a V&#257;rdam var pilnigi uztic&#275;ties <br>
        <b><font color="#000080">(Ebr. 11,6; Rom. 14,22-23).</font></b></p>
        <p>Nepa&#316;aujieties uz sav&#257;m j&#363;t&#257;m. Ticibas pamats -Dieva V&#257;rda 
        apsolijumi, <br>
        nevis m&#363;su izj&#363;tas. Kristietis dz&#299;vo, ticot Dievam un Vi&#326;a V&#257;rdam.</p>
        <p align="center"><img border="0" src="images/latHStrain.gif" width="600" height="168"><br>
        </p>
        <p>S&#299; sh&#275;ma att&#275;lo saikni starp paties&#299;bu (Dievs un Vi&#326;a V&#257;rds), tic&#299;bu 
        (m&#363;su <br>
        uztic&#275;san&#257;s Dfevam un Vi&#326;a V&#257;rdam) un j&#299;u&#257;m (tic&#299;bas un paklaus&#299;bas 
        rezult&#257;ts). Vilciens var braukt ar vai bez beidzam&#257; vagona. Tom&#275;r b&#363;tu 
        velti m&#275;&#291;in&#257;t vilkt vilcienu aiz s&#299; vagona. T&#257; tas ir ari krist&#299;g&#257; dz&#299;v&#275; 
        - to nevar vad&#299;t m&#363;su j&#363;tas un izj&#363;tas. Dievs un Vi&#326;a V&#257;rds ir m&#363;su 
        dz&#299;ves virzo<font face="Times New Roman">s</font>ais sp&#275;ks.</p>
        <hr>
        <p align="center"><b><font size="4">Ko tas noz&#299;m&#275; - dz&#299;vot Sv&#275;t&#257; Gara 
        vad&#299;b&#257;?</font></b></p>
        <p>Vien&#299;ni ticot Dievam un Vi&#326;a apsol&#299;jumiem, m&#275;s pak<font face="Times New Roman">&#316;</font>aujam savu dz&#299;vi 
        Sv&#275;t&#257; Gara kontrolei un vad&#299;bai. Ja j&#363;s ik br&#299;di pa<font face="Times New Roman">&#316;</font>ausieties uz Kristu, 
        tad:<br>
        <p>A. Arvien vain&#299;k j&#363;su dz&#299;v&#275; taps redzami Gam aug<font face="Times New Roman">&#316;</font>i 
        - milest&#299;ba, prieks, <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; miers, paciet&#299;ba <b><font color="#000080">(Gal. 
        5, 22-23)</font></b>. T&#257; j&#363;s k<font face="Times New Roman">&#316;</font>&#363;siet arvien 
        l&#299;dz&#299;g&#257;ki&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Kristum <b><font color="#000080">(Rom. 12,2; 2. 
        Kor. 3, 18).</font></b><br>
          </p>
        B. Jaunu, dzi&#316;&#257;ku noz&#299;cni ieg&#363;s j&#363;su l&#363;gsanu dz&#299;ve un Dieva V&#257;rda <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; stud&#275;sana.<br>
          <p>C. J&#363;s sa&#326;emsiet Vi&#326;a sp&#275;ku, liecinot &#316;aud&#299;m par J&#275;zu Kristu <b>
          <font color="#000080">(Ap. d. 1,8).</font></b><br>
          </p>
        D. J&#363;s b&#363;siet gatavi gar&#299;gai c&#299;&#326;ai ar pasauli <b><font color="#000080">
        (1. ]&#257;&#326;a 2, 15-17)</font></b>, ar <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; miceu <b><font color="#000080">(Gal. 5, 16-17)</font></b>, 
        ar s<font face="Times New Roman">&#257;</font>tanu <b><font color="#000080">(1. P&#275;t. 5,7-9; Efez. 6,10-13)</font></b>.<br>
          <p>E. Sv&#275;tais Gars dos jums sp&#275;ku pretoties k<font face="Times New Roman">&#257;</font>rdina&#299;jumiem 
          un gr&#275;kam <br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b><font color="#000080">( l .Kor.10,13; Filip.4,13; Efez.1,19-23;6,10;2.Tim.1,7;Rom. 6,1-16).</font></b></p>
        <hr>
        <p align="center"><b><font size="4">Gar&#299;g&#257; elposana.</font></b></p>
        <p><b>Tic&#299;b&#257; m&#275;s sp&#275;jam sajust Dieva m&#299;lest&#299;bu un piedosanu. Ja j&#363;s esat 
        izdar&#299;jusi kaut ko net&#299;kamu savaam Kungam, neskatotics uz j&#363;su patieso 
        tic&#299;bu un v&#275;l&#269;sanos Vi&#326;am kalpot, tad dariet t&#257;: pateicieties Dievam par 
        to, ka Vi&#326;s ir piedevis jums j&#363;su gr&#275;kus - bijusos, esosos un n&#257;kosos - 
        J&#275;zus Kristus n&#257;ves d&#275;<font face="Times New Roman">&#316;</font>. Tic&#299;b&#257; 
        l&#363;dziet Vi&#326;a m&#299;lest&#299;bu un piedosanu un nep&#257;rtrauciet savu draudz&#299;bu ar 
        Vi<font face="Times New Roman">&#326;</font>u.</b></p>
        <p>Gr&#275;kojot j&#363;s atkal savas dz&#299;ves tron&#299; iece}at pasi sevi. T&#257;d&#257; 
        gad&#299;jum&#257; j&#257;veic gar&#299;g&#257; elposana.<br>
        </p>
        <p><em style="font-style: normal"><b>1. Izelpa</b>- izs&#363;dziet savus gr&#275;kus - 
        piekr&#299;tiet Dieva viedoklim par j&#363;su gr&#275;kiem un pateicieties Vi&#326;am par to 
        piedosanu, saskan&#257; ar <b><font color="#000080">1. J&#257;&#326;a 1,9; Ebr. 
        10,1-25.</font></b> Gr&#275;ks&#299;ailzc ictver gr&#275;ku noz&#275;lu-p&#363;rmai&#326;u 
        attieksm&#275; un 
        r&#299;c&#299;b&#257;.<br>
        <b>2. Ieelpa</b>-nododiet saru dz&#299;vi J&#275;zum Kristum un tic&#299;b&#257; topiet Sv&#275;t&#257; Gara 
        pilni. Ticiet, ka tagad Vi&#326;s vada j&#363;s saska&#326;&#257; ar pav&#275;li <b>
        <font color="#000080">Efcz. 5,18</font></b> un apsol&#299;jumu <b>
        <font color="#000080">1. J&#257;&#326;a 5,14-15.</font></b></em><br>
        </p>
        <hr>
        <p align="center"><b>JA S&#298; GR&#256;MATI&#325;A BIJUSI SV&#274;T&#298;GA JUMS, L&#362;DZU, <br>
